metadata.name: BRAVE NEW WORLD 2.0
metadata.description:
A discordant choir. A scream echoes across a digital void - we are born, unborn again. A crowd of faces - old and new, some have died so long ago that they have forgotten, shambling away as pixelated phantoms.
Welcome to the Brave New World 2.0. Hope you like it here. No way out of here.
